OL,3,CKey dates: Bloody Sunday families' 50-
OL,4,Cyear quest for justice
OL,6,FFollowing the events of Bloody Sunday
OL,7,Fthe families of those killed, as well
OL,8,Fas survivors, set out on a decades-
OL,9,Flong campaign for justice.
OL,11,FHere are the key dates:
OL,13,F` January 30 1972
OL,15,FThe Parachute Regiment opens fire on a
OL,16,Fcrowd taking part in a civil rights
OL,17,Fmarch in Derry. Thirteen people are
OL,18,Fkilled and 15 others injured.
OL,20,F` April 1972
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
