OL,3,CKey dates: Bloody Sunday families' 50-
OL,4,Cyear quest for justice
OL,6,FAn inquiry led by Lord Chief Justice
OL,7,FLord Widgery supports the soldiers'
OL,8,Fversion of events, that they were
OL,9,Freturning fire. Bereaved families
OL,10,Fdismiss the report as a whitewash.
OL,12,F` February 1992
OL,14,FFirst meeting of the Bloody Sunday
OL,15,FJustice Campaign.
OL,17,F` January 1994
OL,19,FThe campaign writes to prime minister
OL,20,FJohn Major seeking a full independent
OL,21,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
