OL,8,FMr Major refuses because there has
OL,9,Falready been a public inquiry by Lord
OL,10,FWidgery.
OL,12,F` January 1997
OL,14,FA 40,000-signature petition calling
OL,15,Ffor a new inquiry is delivered by the
OL,16,Fcampaign to 10 Downing Street.
OL,18,F` January 1998
