OL,6,FPrime Minister Tony Blair announces a
OL,7,Fnew inquiry, with Lord Saville of
OL,8,FNewdigate appointed to chair the probe.
OL,10,F` November 2000-September 2002
OL,12,FThe Saville Inquiry hears oral
OL,13,Fevidence.
OL,15,F` August 2001
OL,17,FSoldiers announce they will seek a
OL,18,Fjudicial review of the decision of the
OL,19,Finquiry that military witnesses must
OL,20,Fgive their evidence in Derry.
