OL,3,CKey dates: Bloody Sunday families' 50-
OL,4,Cyear quest for justice
OL,6,FLord Saville delivers his findings
OL,7,Fthat there was no justification for
OL,8,Fshooting any of those killed or
OL,9,Fwounded. Prime minister David Cameron
OL,10,Fissues a public apology. saying the
OL,11,Fkillings were "unjustified and
OL,12,Funjustifiable".
OL,14,F` July 2012
OL,16,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,17,Fformally launches a murder
OL,18,Finvestigation into the events of
OL,19,FBloody Sunday.
OL,21,F` September-October 2018
