OL,6,FThe first Ministry of Defence
OL,7,Fcompensation settlement in relation to
OL,8,FBloody Sunday victims is awarded.
OL,10,F` March 2019
OL,12,FThe Public Prosecution Service (PPS)
OL,13,Fannounces that one former soldier,
OL,14,Fknown as Soldier F, will be prosecuted
OL,15,Ffor the murders of James Wray and
OL,16,FWilliam McKinney and the attempted
OL,17,Fmurders of Joseph Friel, Michael
OL,18,FQuinn, Joe Mahon and Patrick O'Donnell.
