OL,3,CKey dates: Bloody Sunday families' 50-
OL,4,Cyear quest for justice
OL,6,FThe PPS announces it is discontinuing
OL,7,Fthe prosecution of Soldier F for the
OL,8,Fmurders of James Wray and William
OL,9,FMcKinney amid concerns that the case
OL,10,Fcould collapse in light of a separate
OL,11,Fcourt ruling on the admissibility of
OL,12,Fevidence which caused the collapse of
OL,13,Fanother Troubles murder trial
OL,14,Finvolving two military veterans. The
OL,15,FMcKinney family signal their intent to
OL,16,Fchallenge the PPS decision on Solider
OL,17,FF in the courts.
OL,19,F` September 2021
