OL,3,CKey dates: Bloody Sunday families' 50-
OL,4,Cyear quest for justice
OL,6,FThe various legal challenges against
OL,7,Fthe PPS are heard together before
OL,8,Fthree senior judges, including the
OL,9,Foriginal decisions not to prosecute
OL,10,Ffive soldiers. Judgment is reserved.
OL,12,F` March 2022
OL,14,FThe judges quash the PPS decision to
OL,15,Fdiscontinue the prosecution of Soldier
OL,16,FF and order prosecutors to reconsider.
OL,18,FThe other legal challenges against PPS
OL,19,Fdecisions not to take prosecutions
OL,20,Fagainst several other veterans were
OL,21,Fdismissed by the court.
