OL,6,FSoldier F appears in court for the
OL,7,Ffirst time since the prosecution
OL,8,Fcommenced. He sits in the witness box
OL,9,Fat Belfast Crown Court, with a thick
OL,10,Ffloor-to-ceiling blue curtain
OL,11,Fshielding him from the main body of
OL,12,Fthe court to protect his anonymity.
